<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset your Password</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { background-color: #ffffff; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .title { color: #333333; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .text { color: #555555; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .button-container { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .button { background-color: #1a237e; color: white !important; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
        .notice { background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #f9a825; padding: 12px 16px; color: #5d4037; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .footer { color: #999999; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding-top: 20px; }
        .fallback-link { word-break: break-all; color: #1a237e; font-size: 13px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{brand.emailHeader}}" alt="ManekHR" style="max-width:240px;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto 16px;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;" />
            <h1 class="title">Reset your password</h1>
        </div>

        <p class="text">Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p class="text">We received a request to reset the password for your ManekHR account. Click the button below to choose a new password.</p>

        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset password</a>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
            This link expires in <strong>{{expiresInMinutes}} minutes</strong> and can be used only once. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password will remain unchanged.
        </div>

        <p class="text" style="margin-top: 28px;">Trouble with the button? Copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p class="fallback-link">{{resetUrl}}</p>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 ManekHR. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
